*****info map***
-=  Many thanks to those who has inspired me on creation of this card.
The card has turned out rather quite good.

Two towers with which there is an excellent review of all card as from outside terrorists and counter-terrorists. The small shed and a tower on the centre with an interesting counter :), 
but not so that and simply to reach it...
There is a water drain with its characteristic floor.
Are available so excellent places for butchers, well and to simply steam of excellent places for optics :) 
Grenade on the centre :) 
Well and for a relaxation and calmness on a card sing birdies :) 
- max players 46
